{"id":"G-001","split":"dev","subject":"ENG-S","grade_band":"高中","doc_type":"jiangyi","difficulty":0.5,"question_type":"concept","query":"虚拟语气里，与现在事实相反时动词怎么变？","query_variants":["与现在事实相反的if从句用什么时态"],"metadata_filters":{"subject":"ENG-S","doc_type":null,"difficulty_max":0.8},"expected_sources":[{"source_file":"vault/3_教辅资料/高中英语/语法/虚拟语气.md","section_title":"与现在事实相反的虚拟语气","knowledge_point_id":"ENG-KP-03-01"}],"relevant_chunk_ids":["d496f3c8-d038-006d-f555-8c7955b4577e"],"ground_truth_answer":"条件从句用过去式（be动词用were），主句用would/could/should/might + 动词原形。","must_include_points":["从句过去式","be用were","主句would/could/should/might + 原形"],"forbidden_points":["主句用过去式"],"answer_format":"definition","eval_notes":"已绑定真实 chunk_id"}
{"id":"G-002","split":"dev","subject":"ENG-S","grade_band":"高中","doc_type":"jiangyi","difficulty":0.6,"question_type":"error_fix","query":"I wish I am taller 这句话错在哪里？","query_variants":["wish从句时态错误怎么改"],"metadata_filters":{"subject":"ENG-S","doc_type":null,"difficulty_max":0.9},"expected_sources":[{"source_file":"vault/3_教辅资料/高中英语/语法/虚拟语气.md","section_title":"wish 宾语从句","knowledge_point_id":"ENG-KP-03-02"}],"relevant_chunk_ids":["81bcda32-5e42-297c-04a1-ccac3c529537"],"ground_truth_answer":"wish后宾语从句表示与现在事实相反，应把am改为were：I wish I were taller。","must_include_points":["wish后从句","与现在相反","am改为were"],"forbidden_points":["改为was"],"answer_format":"analysis","eval_notes":"改错题"}
{"id":"G-009","split":"dev","subject":"MATH-S","grade_band":"高中","doc_type":"jiangyi","difficulty":0.5,"question_type":"concept","query":"什么是等差数列的通项公式？","query_variants":["arithmetic sequence general term"],"metadata_filters":{"subject":"MATH-S","doc_type":null,"difficulty_max":0.7},"expected_sources":[{"source_file":"vault/3_教辅资料/高中数学/数列/等差数列.md","section_title":"通项公式","knowledge_point_id":"MATH-KP-02-01"}],"relevant_chunk_ids":["3b5a9196-5e38-5939-d01d-234036932568"],"ground_truth_answer":"等差数列通项公式：an = a1 + (n-1)d，其中a1为首项，d为公差。","must_include_points":["an=a1+(n-1)d","a1首项","d公差"],"forbidden_points":["an=a1*d^n"],"answer_format":"formula","eval_notes":"公式检索"}
